{"tid":1942299,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何栢良警告 : 不戒嚴，醫院管理局下星期會崩潰","createTime":"2020-03-25T03:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T03:57:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"812fd141ff748e9398a1ae04986ea39187760853","tid":1942299,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200325/photo/bkn-20200325101934483-0325_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200325105137\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200325%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200325101934483-0325_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200325105137&h=0e1d87c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情加劇，香港近期不少新增個案均去過酒吧消遣或參加逾百人的派對。香港大學感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良今早(25日)接受電台訪問時警告，本地確診人數在過去3周多了10倍，倘若政府不全線推出戒嚴級別措施，阻止人群聚集，預計醫院管理局下星期會崩潰，醫療體系將會失守。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，現時香港出現沒有感染源頭的本地個案，可能已發生第三重傳播，必需中斷傳播鏈，政府不可以再推出單一措施，亦不應再「半桶水」及「擠牙膏」，並舉例指歐洲不少醫護死於新冠肺炎，若不推出措施，擔心當年沙士的情況重演，本地醫護人員會重蹈覆轍。他又認為政府禁止非香港居民入境，應該要包括外地傭工。 <br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200325/bkn-20200325101934483-0325_00822_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"397e66d955c87d793349039b1133a1ee1a6d66ad","tid":1942299,"uid":187192,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:46:13.000Z","msg":"又9up 笑撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d60a5e229ca428d10d3e0f1ee5a8c663140fc5f","tid":1942299,"uid":200070,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:49:50.000Z","msg":"香港班醫護罷工辭職都唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班奴隸咁忠心幫高層抹屎<br />\n支爆先都未到香港醫療崩潰<br />\n真係9up唔洗本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1d6e056ba4945a4dc8f3cc9c89167d01304118","tid":1942299,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc95e7819b44ca9f9cbe4d06d62ac43413164d8e","tid":1942299,"uid":52897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:57:18.000Z","msg":"罷工囉"},{"pid":"b4a9fe51424ae774f1cd24883fb3237ab15e8930","tid":1942299,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:57:29.000Z","msg":"推"}]}